If you live in California, vote against <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/California_Proposition_8_(2008)">Proposition 8</a>. Prop 8 adds this line to the CA Constitution:
<blockquote>
Only marriage between a man and a woman is valid or recognized in California.
</blockquote>

